description: As a user, I want to import reviews from multiple platforms so that I can manage them in Feedspace.

elements.name: Login and Import reviews from all platforms sequentially

steps.name: I navigate to the Feedspace sign-in page
I enter the email "test1235@mailinator.com"
I click on "Send Sign-In Code" button
I fetch the OTP from Mailinator for user "test1235"
I enter the retrieved OTP
I should be logged in successfully
